---
title: Rich & Saucy Pork Scotch Tomato Stew with Garlic Rice & Parsley
description: If you’re planning to stay in with a cosy home-cooked dinner, then this stew fits the criteria. Let your slow cooker do the work,
transforming tender pork and veggies into a hearty, tomato-based delight. Dig in and enjoy a bowl of pure comfort.
